<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:56:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么俄罗斯可能对中国在中亚的“一带一路”计划热情高涨</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258142/why-russia-might-be-warming-chinas-belt-and-road-plans-central-asia?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>俄罗斯官员关于“一带一路”与欧亚集团一体化的言论标志着对中国战略的新兴趣，莫斯科曾将其视为对其主导地位的挑战。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258142/why-russia-might-be-warming-chinas-belt-and-road-plans-central-asia?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>华南地区仍遭遇强降雨袭击 多日来第二次洪水警报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258150/southern-china-still-lashed-heavy-rains-triggering-second-flood-alert-many-days?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家气象局连续第二天对多个省份发布暴雨蓝色警报，几天前，江西的反常暴雨和大风导致七人死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 13:28:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258150/southern-china-still-lashed-heavy-rains-triggering-second-flood-alert-many-days?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>多边的小成功提醒我们为什么大国必须合作</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3258128/small-multilateral-successes-remind-us-why-great-powers-must-cooperate?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>各国必须言行一致，解决气候变化和人工智能监管等紧迫问题。尽管联合国等机构陷入瘫痪，但北极理事会和国际海底管理局等组织正在取得进展。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3258128/small-multilateral-successes-remind-us-why-great-powers-must-cooperate?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾前领导人马英九在中国大陆访问期间否认日本对钓鱼岛的主权主张</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258143/taiwans-former-leader-ma-ying-jeou-rejects-japans-claims-diaoyu-islands-during-mainland-china-trip?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据新华社报道，对大陆友好的台湾前总统在“和平之旅”期间在古皇城西安展示明代手稿后否认有争议的钓鱼岛是日本领土。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258143/taiwans-former-leader-ma-ying-jeou-rejects-japans-claims-diaoyu-islands-during-mainland-china-trip?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国游客斥巨资庆祝2019年以来最赚钱的清明节</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258138/chinese-travellers-spend-big-mark-most-profitable-ching-ming-festival-2019?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周六结束的三天假期，国内出行量超过 1.19 亿人次，收入接近 540 亿元人民币，远高于大流行前的水平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 10:59:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258138/chinese-travellers-spend-big-mark-most-profitable-ching-ming-festival-2019?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>解决中美关系必须以老百姓的生活为中心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3258113/fix-us-china-relations-we-must-centre-lives-ordinary-people?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>到中国旅行让美国学生体会到了这个国家的复杂性，并与中国人民分享了欢乐的时刻。美国人和中国人之间的面对面互动必须保留，即使是在两国政府之间的关系变得更加紧张的情况下。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 09:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3258113/fix-us-china-relations-we-must-centre-lives-ordinary-people?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国华为凭借突破性的人工智能模型“知己”再次挑战传统天气预报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257969/chinas-huawei-challenging-traditional-weather-forecasting-again-time-groundbreaking-ai-model-zhiji?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>基于华为盘古天气的突破性人工智能模型知己可以提供五天的预报，精度仅为3公里。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 09:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257969/chinas-huawei-challenging-traditional-weather-forecasting-again-time-groundbreaking-ai-model-zhiji?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国、英国、澳大利亚“准备就扩大奥库斯安全协议进行谈判”以威慑中国，日本可能是候选者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258126/us-uk-australia-set-talks-expanding-aukus-security-pact-deter-china-japan-likely-candidate?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据《金融时报》援引知情人士的话报道，会谈将涉及该协议的“第二支柱”，涵盖量子计算、海底、高超音速、人工智能和网络技术。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258126/us-uk-australia-set-talks-expanding-aukus-security-pact-deter-china-japan-likely-candidate?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列的外交关系因加沙战争而动摇，台湾看到了缓和的机会</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258086/israels-foreign-ties-falter-amid-war-gaza-taiwan-sees-chance-cosy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>台北将中东冲突视为学习以色列国防战略和培养友好关系的机会。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 07:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258086/israels-foreign-ties-falter-amid-war-gaza-taiwan-sees-chance-cosy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国、菲律宾、日本和澳大利亚举行联合军演，解放军在南海巡逻</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258120/pla-patrols-south-china-sea-us-philippines-japan-and-australia-hold-joint-military-drills?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国举行空中和海上战斗巡逻，与美国及其盟国旨在支持“自由开放的印度太平洋”的全面演习同时进行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:43:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258120/pla-patrols-south-china-sea-us-philippines-japan-and-australia-hold-joint-military-drills?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国李强回应珍妮特·耶伦“产能过剩”担忧，美国不应将贸易问题政治化</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258114/china-and-us-shouldnt-avoid-tough-conversations-janet-yellen-tells-li-qiang-frank-and-productive?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>