mp.com/news/china/article/3258074/chinese-expatriate-entrepreneurs-find-new-gold-rush-destination-mexico?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>为了寻求经济机会，中国商人建立了熙熙攘攘的批发市场，销售中国制造的商品，并应对墨西哥供应商偶尔的抵制。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 15:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258074/chinese-expatriate-entrepreneurs-find-new-gold-rush-destination-mexico?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>